summary: All the QA Test Containers available at the start of your game with using the console.
descriptionHtml:
The QA containers hold just about every item in the game. They are located in a satchel in the Torturers Chamber in Hegen that you go through at the start of the game.

*Warning: The All Enchanted Armors and All Enchanted Weapons containers take a while to load, you will think your game has frozen but just give it time and it should load up.*

*Warning 2: There are several quest items in the containers that could break a quest.*

This is a just simple mod, altering this one container for those that don\'t want to use the console. It shouldn\'t interfere with any other mods.
author: Gawl40
